  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee ne iſſalks ned̄ iſſlahps / tehs arri ne ſpeedths\nned̄ Karſtums ned̄ ta Saule/ jo winnu Apschehlotajs tohs\nwaddihs/ un weddihs tohs weegſinam pee teem Uhdens Awo\nteem."
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un es darrischu wiſſus mannus Kalnuß par weenn Zek\ntu/ un manni ſtaigati Zelti taps pa-augſtinati."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Redſi / ſchee nahks no tahkenes/ un rangi/ ſchee no See-\nmeta Puſſes/ un no Juhras / un ſchee no tab̄ Senneß Sinim."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Gawilejeet juhs Debbe-\ntis/ un preezajes tu Semme/\ndarrajt weenu Trohſnt juhs\nKalni ar Gawileschaun/ jo tas\nKUNGS irr tawus Landis ee-\npreezinajs/ un apſchehlofees pahr\nfaweem Behdigeem."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet Ziana ſakka: Tas\nKUNGS irr mann atſtabjis/\nun tas KUNGS irr mannis\naigmirſts."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Warr arridsan weena\nSeeva ſawu ſibſchanu Behrun\nateſmirſt/ ka wizza ue apſcheh-\nlotohs pabr to Dehlu ſawas\nMerfas? Ir jopſchu winna to\naiſmirſtu / temehr es tewis ne\naiſmirſichu/"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Redſi/ (mannas) Roh-\nkäs eſmu es tewi rakſtije: Tawi\nMuhti irr weennmehr manná\nPreckſcha."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tawi Nemmeschi ſteigſecs/ bet tawi Pohstitaji un Sa-\nlausitaji iſces no tewim nohſt."
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pazell tawas Azzis wiſſ.\napkahrt/ un rangi/ wiſſi ſchee fa-\npulzinajabs un nahk pee tewis.\nTik teeschaun ka es dſihwoju/ taſ-\nka tas KUNGS : Tu tapſt ar\nſcheem wiſſeem apgebrbts/ itt ka\nar weennu Glihtumu/ un apmet-\ntiſecs tohs ka weena Bruhte."
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tawas pohſtas un\nweentutas Weetas/ un tawa no-\npohſtita Senne taps tew nu\nwiſſai ſchaura/ tik dauds Eedſih-\nwotaju deht / un tawi Aprihjeji\natkahps tahſu no tewim."
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzihs tee * Behrni\n(pehz taween pirmeem) jud-\nduſcheem (Behrneem) preeſſch\ntawahin Aufim: Ta Weeta irr\npreeſſch mannim ſchaura / wir-\nſees man/ ka es dſihwoht warnu.\n* Ta Judu Draudſe tohp weenai Seewai\nlihdſinara, kas Deewam Behrnus dſemdeja, ka-\nmehr ra nu eekſeh Tizzibas us Kristu pa-\nlikke, us ko ta Bauſliba winnu rahdija, tad\npatikke winna Deewam, bet kad ra atkaſpe,\ntad dewe Deews winnai weenu St Kirſchanas-\nGrahmatu, ka winnas Behni tappe laudeti,\nun Deews peenehme few Behrnns no teem Pa-\nganeem, kas zaur Kristus un to Apustulo Mah-\nzibu winnas Klehpi d(e)minati un winnas\nBehrni noſaukti tappē:"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tu fazziſi tawā Sir-\ndi: Kas irr man ichohs dſeindi-\nnajs? Jo es eſmu bes Behrneem/\nweentuka/ es biju Zeetuma we-\nſta un iſklihdusi/ kas tad ichohs\nman irr uſandſinajs ? Rangi /\nes biju atſtahta weena/ kur tad\nſchee bijaz"
    }
  ],
